Sur qui me 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #E">vangerois-je </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D">vengerois-je </rdg>
      </app>
en ce mal-heur 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">extréme&#160;? </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">extrême&#160;? </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

    </sp>
    <sp>
      <speaker><app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">ETEOCLE. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">ETEOCLE </rdg>
      </app></speaker>
<l n="848">
Vos ennemis, Creon, sont ceux de Thebes 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">mesme, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">même, </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="849.1">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">Vangez-la, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">Vangés-la, </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#D">Vengez-la, </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">vangez&#160;vous. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B">vangez-vous. </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#C">vangés-vous. </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#D">vengez-vous. </rdg>
      </app>
</l>
    </sp>
    <sp>
      <speaker>CREON.</speaker>
<l n="849.2">
Ah&#160;! dans 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">ces </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">ses </rdg>
      </app>
Ennemis, </l>
<l n="850">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">Je </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">Ie </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">trouve </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">trouue </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">vostre </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">vôtre </rdg>
      </app>
Frere, &amp; 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">je </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">ie </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">trouve </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">trouue </rdg>
      </app>
mon Fils. </l>

<l n="851">
Dois-je verser mon sang, ou 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">respandre </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">répandre </rdg>
      </app>
le vostre&#160;? </l>

<l n="852">
Et dois-je perdre 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">un </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">vn </rdg>
      </app>
Fils pour en 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #E">vanger </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D">venger </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">un </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">vn </rdg>
      </app>
autre&#160;? </l>

<l n="853">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">Seigneur </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">Seigneur, </rdg>
      </app>
mon sang m’est cher, le 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #D #E">vostre </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">vôtre </rdg>
      </app>
m’est sacré, </l>

<l n="854">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">Seray-je </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">Seray-ie </rdg>
      </app>
sacrilege ou bien dénaturé&#160;? </l>

<l n="855">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">Soüilleray-je </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">Soüillerai-je </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#D">Souilleray-je </rdg>
      </app>
ma main 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">d’un </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">d’vn </rdg>
      </app>
sang que je 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#E">revere, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">reuere, </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">revere&#160;? </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="856">
Seray-je parricide, afin 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #E">d’estre </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D">d’être </rdg>
      </app>
bon Pere&#160;? </l>

<l n="857">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">Un </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">Vn </rdg>
      </app>
si cruel secours ne me peut soulager, </l>

<l n="858">
Et ce seroit me perdre au lieu de me 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #E">vanger. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D">venger. </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="859">
Tout le soulagement 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">ou </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">où </rdg>
      </app>
ma douleur aspire, </l>

<l n="860">
C’est qu’au moins mes mal-heurs 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">servent </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">seruent </rdg>
      </app>
à vostre 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">Empire, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">Empire. </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="861">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">Je </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">Ie </rdg>
      </app>
me 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #D #E">consoleray </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">consolerai </rdg>
      </app>
si ce Fils que je plains, </l>

<l n="862">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #E">Assure </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D">Assûre </rdg>
      </app>
par sa mort le repos des Thebains. </l>

<l n="863">
